data.description: This piece of paradise can be yours!!! Welcome home to Paradise Place. This 2/2 waterfront property has so many features to offer.  One of them being the beautiful views with ocean access that leads to South Fork of the St Lucie River with fixed bridges that have 6' clearance.  Other outdoor features include a dock, deck, boat lift for a small boat/canoe and a cabana.  You will enjoy Florida style entertaining year round with the beautiful outdoor area and the wraparound family room. The deep two car garage has a lot of space for storage. There are no leases allowed for the first 2 years, and after that only annual leases will be accepted. **UPDATE** Flooring & new plywood installed throughout home!! Completion of improvements in master bathroom are underway.
